OL,3,CWhy some African Americans are leaving
OL,4,Cthe United States for Ghana
OL,6,FIn many ways, travelling to Ghana five
OL,7,Fyears after this scheme launched
OL,8,Fmarked my own year of return.
OL,10,FGhana was the place I was born, and it
OL,11,Fis where I spent the first half of my
OL,12,Flife.
OL,14,FMy parents, like so many others, had
OL,15,Fmigrated west in hope of better
OL,16,Fopportunities, and so I couldn't help
OL,17,Fbut wonder why anyone would leave the
OL,18,Feconomic prospects that the United
OL,19,FKingdom or the United States had to
OL,20,Foffer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
