OL,3,CWhy some African Americans are leaving
OL,4,Cthe United States for Ghana
OL,6,FITV News' Reporter Kaf Okpattah
OL,7,Ftravels to Ghana, where a scheme
OL,8,Fencouraging African diasporas to visit
OL,9,Fthe country was considered an
OL,10,Foverwhelming success
OL,12,FThis question was quickly answered
OL,13,Fwhen I met Morris Briggers at Mabel's
OL,14,FTable in Elmina - a popular hang out
OL,15,Fspot for diasporas in Ghana.
OL,17,FMorris had served his country for
OL,18,Fyears as a US Navy Seal, but after
OL,19,Fjust a few minutes of speaking to him
OL,20,Fit was clear he didn't feel his
OL,21,Fcountry had served him.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
