OL,3,CWhy some African Americans are leaving
OL,4,Cthe United States for Ghana
OL,6,F"Oh, somebody's going to get shot for
OL,7,Fsure tonight," Morris responded. "In
OL,8,Fall of the cities that I lived in, in
OL,9,Fthe United States somebody will get
OL,10,Fshot."
OL,12,FHe's right, of course. The US ranks
OL,13,Fsecond for gun related deaths
OL,14,Faccording to the World Population
OL,15,FReview.
OL,17,FWhen you also consider that the US has
OL,18,Fa history of black people being shot
OL,19,Fand killed by the police, you can see
OL,20,Fwhy Morris felt safer in Ghana, and he
OL,21,Fwasn't the only one.
