OL,3,CWhy some African Americans are leaving
OL,4,Cthe United States for Ghana
OL,6,FRashad is a US citizen who was
OL,7,Ffollowing Morris's lead in making
OL,8,FGhana his new home.
OL,10,FHe said: "There are so many things
OL,11,Fthat go on in the United States that
OL,12,Fmarginalise black Americans.
OL,14,F"Being on the African continent,
OL,15,Fspecifically Ghana right now... It's a
OL,16,Fsense of real freedom, real enjoyment
OL,17,Fof seeing what black empowerment can
OL,18,Fface."
