OL,3,CWhy some African Americans are leaving
OL,4,Cthe United States for Ghana
OL,6,FIt's clear that both Morris and Rashad
OL,7,Fhave given up on the American dream
OL,8,Fthat so famously defines their
OL,9,Fhomeland, and they've traded it for a
OL,10,Fdream life in Ghana - and it is very
OL,11,Fmuch a dream life.
OL,13,FThey have the power of the US dollar
OL,14,Fin their bank accounts, making them
OL,15,Ffar richer than the locals here.
OL,16,FRashad has even been appointed a local
OL,17,Fchief, giving him a sort of royalty
OL,18,Fstatus.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
