OL,3,CWhy some African Americans are leaving
OL,4,Cthe United States for Ghana
OL,6,FThere's no denying that many African
OL,7,FAmericans were relocating to Ghana to
OL,8,Freconnect with their roots, and to
OL,9,Fescape the racism they may have
OL,10,Fexperienced in the US. But not
OL,11,Feveryone is convinced by this motive.
OL,13,FDr Ashley Milton has spent most of her
OL,14,Fadult life working across the African
OL,15,Fcontinent. Her home is currently a two
OL,16,Fbed-apartment in Ghana's capital,
OL,17,FAccra, and it is there she shares with
OL,18,Fme the reservations she has about some
OL,19,Fof her fellow diasporans.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
