OL,3,CWhy some African Americans are leaving
OL,4,Cthe United States for Ghana
OL,6,F"Different cultures are going to live
OL,7,Fdifferently", she said.
OL,9,F"By virtue of that difference, African
OL,10,FAmericans are going to live a
OL,11,Fdifferent lifestyle than Ghanaians.
OL,13,F"If you're not interested in the
OL,14,Fculture, the customs, the history, the
OL,15,Flanguage, the lineage and what has
OL,16,Fgone down on these lands, then you're
OL,17,Fjust a neocolonialist and you really
OL,18,Fshouldn't come."
