OL,3,CWhy some African Americans are leaving
OL,4,Cthe United States for Ghana
OL,6,FAs I said goodbye to Ashley, I
OL,7,Fpondered over what she had told me,
OL,8,Fthe possibility that this migration
OL,9,Ffrom the US to Ghana may in part be
OL,10,Fdriven by opportunism.
OL,12,FAnd if that were the case, then the
OL,13,Fincreased purchasing power
OL,14,F'diasporans' hold could have a
OL,15,Fdetrimental effect on locals who don't
OL,16,Fshare that wealth.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
