OL,3,CWhy some African Americans are leaving
OL,4,Cthe United States for Ghana
OL,6,FRegardless of how you feel about the
OL,7,Fmotives of African-American diasporans
OL,8,Fin Ghana, one can't deny that the Year
OL,9,Fof Return has been somewhat of a
OL,10,Fsuccess.
