OL,3,CWhy some African Americans are leaving
OL,4,Cthe United States for Ghana
OL,6,FFive years on the movement is still
OL,7,Fgrowing, with busloads of Americans
OL,8,Ftravelling to Ghana to take part in a
OL,9,Ftraditional naming ceremony - swapping
OL,10,Fout their slave descendant names for a
OL,11,FGhanaian one like Kwesi, or Kweku.
OL,13,FIt's clear that the Year of Return has
OL,14,Fincreased Ghana's sphere of influence
OL,15,Fin the West, placing itself as a sort
OL,16,Fof haven for those with African
OL,17,Fheritage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
