OL,3,CWhy some African Americans are leaving
OL,4,Cthe United States for Ghana
OL,6,FAt a time when US politics is
OL,7,Fincredibly divisive, there will
OL,8,Fundoubtedly be African Americans who
OL,9,Fare unhappy with who their president
OL,10,Fis or what their country is like
OL,12,FFor them, at least, there is some
OL,13,Fcomfort in knowing they will always
OL,14,Fhave a home in Ghana.
